    "The SVM used in the INTERSPEECH 2009 emotion challenge is a linear SVM that was trained using a relatively limited quantity of labeled data.",
    "Additionally, four semisupervised learning approaches-the self-training and denoising autoencoder (DAE) combined with SVM, the SSAE, and the semisupervised ladder autoencoder (SS-LAE)-are compared with our suggested methods.",
